I have made skills for a long while, so they have been pretty easy to make the bases for.
[s]However, I have never made a combat system before, so it definitely poses a challenge. [/s] It was hard, however, it wasn't that bad. Combat is entity based. So pvp, pvn, nvp, and nvn all work fine.

